title: Metallica - Woodstock 99.divx
description:
I was clearing the dust off my VHS tapes from the 90s and what do you know I come upon the Woodstock 99 recordings I made from Pay Per View.  It is a large file size, but it played just fine with Roxio 8 Cineplayer with the Divx.com codec on Vixta.  I also was able to burn it with PowerISO directly from file and watch the entire hour and fifty minutes with my generic Magnavox Divx stand alone.  The quality is VHS - Divx 48 Khz sound.

File Size:  2.69 GB
Length:     1:50
File:       Divx 6.8

JerryTJr.com
